# This GitHub Action and GH Extension is used to set up repositories with the following:

- Milestones
- Version Tagging
- Multi Architecture Container Images
- Pushing to Container Registries

```plaintext
{REPO}/.
 │
└── .github/workflows/
    ├── milestones.yml              # Only run on specific conditions
    ├── tagging.yml                 # Only tag if version changes
    ├── docker-ghcr-push.yml        # Pushes Docker images on tags
    ├── multi-arch-build.yml        # Builds multi-arch images on tags or releases
└── GitVersion.yml              # GitVersion versioning rules
```